How to use PrereqMe
-------------------

GET /
	Get the status of the API
GET /schools/
	Get all the schools PrereqMe knows about
GET /schools/<slug>
	Get the information of a single school
GET /schools/<slug>/departments/
	Get all the departments a school has
GET /schools/<slug>/departments/<abbreviation>
	Get the information of a single department
GET /schools/<slug>/departments/<abbreviation>/courses/
	Get all the courses in a department
GET /schools/<slug>/departments/<abbreviation>/courses/<number>
	Get the information of a single course
